.github
.idea
docs
target
**/target
project/project
.venv
.ruff_cache
node_modules
**/node_modules
*.md
mise.toml
mise.local.toml
docker-compose.yaml
.env
.env.example
.coderabbit.yaml
lefthook.yml
src/test
